Output dbt.gif
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1080
Set Height 200
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/.local/bin:/tmp/bftest-dbt/venv/bin:$PATH BACKFILL_API=https://backfill.sh DBT_PROFILES_DIR=/tmp/bftest-dbt/proj PYTHONWARNINGS=ignore && cd /tmp/bftest-dbt/proj && clear"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show
Type "bf dbt run"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 38s
